  "title": "Dental Surgery Assistant (Junior)-6681",
  "description": "<p><strong>Dental Surgery Assistant</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $2500 - $2700</strong></p><p><strong>Working hours: 5.5 days Monday - Friday | 9am – 6pm. Saturday 9am – 1pm</strong></p><p><strong>Location: Walking distance from Novena MRT </strong></p><p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><ul><li>Assisting doctor in all dental procedures (scaling, filling, root canal, dental surgery, implants, crowns and bridges, braces etc)</li><li>Sterilization of equipment and keeping clinic clean and tidy </li><li>Assist dental surgeon encompasses a wide range of procedures from preparing the various required and ensuring the proper instruments and equipment are available</li><li>Take, expose, and mount high-quality dental radiographs</li><li>Assist in jaw surgeries and wisdom teeth surgeries</li><li>Welcome patients and get them situated in the appropriate treatment room.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>At least one year experience in this field</li></ul><p>CHUAH ZHI XING | Reg No: R25136681</p><p>THE SUPREME HR ADVISORY PTE LTD | EA No: 14C7279</p>",
